Berkshire Hathaway HomeServices NW Real Estate

data.description: Beautiful Custom Home built in 2006. This home is three levels and includes three bedrooms on the upper level including a Primary Bedroom with gorgeous views, a recessed ceiling, walk-in closet, and attached luxurious bathroom suite.  Primary Bathroom suite includes a new custom glass shower door, walk-in shower, updated shower floor tiles, dual sink custom vanities and a jetted bathtub. The second and third bedroom share a Jack and Jill bathroom with a custom vanity.  Main level has an office with built-ins, plantation shutters and a custom coffered ceiling.  The dining room and living room share a natural gas fireplace perfect for fall days.  The custom Kitchen opens to the family room and includes granite counter tops, stainless steel dishwasher, a granite island with a cooktop and attached dining nook.  The third level has a full bathroom with shower and separate entrance from the garage. Also on the third floor is Cinema Room/Bonus Room with a wet bar and an overhead projector that stays with the home. Storage room on third level of home was previously used as a work-out room.  Third level has a walk-in sauna. You don't want to miss the oversized coated three car garage.  From the living room and primary bedroom, you can enjoy watching the sunset from your deck. Don't miss you chance to own a custom home on a large lot and too many amenities to list. Seller Incentives up to 3% for a Rate Buydown including possible permanent rate.  Current rates were in the mid-fives but of course rate depends current rates available.  Call if you are interested or have questions.
